<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 03-05-01 - Lubrication to the Intermediate Steering Column Upper U-Joint</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi030501" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>03-05-01</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>July, 2003</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>STEERING</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Lubrication to the Intermediate Steering Column Upper U-Joint</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>4200</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4300</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4400</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7300</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7400</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7500</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7600</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8500</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8600</truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Information from the field indicates that the upper u-joint on the intermediate steering column is
                    not being lubricated during maintenance intervals.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <svcproc svcproctype="repair" graphiccount="2">
            <title>Service Procedure</title>
            <para>The u-joint is located near the power distribution center, on the left inner fender panel, as shown in
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0305011">Figure 1</hotlnk>
                . Sufficient grease should be inserted to purge the old grease so that clean new grease is visible at
                each u-joint trunnion. The steering column may need to be turned slightly to make the zerk fitting
                accessible (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0305012">Figure 2</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <para>For lubrication intervals refer to the Operator Manual for the model being serviced.</para>
            <figure id="f0305011" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g0305011.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="392px"/>
                <caption>Figure 1. Location of Steering U-Joint</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="f0305012" figsize="pg-wide">
                <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g0305012.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="352px"
                         scalefitheight="352px"/>
                <caption>Figure 2. Arrow Indicates Zerk Fitting</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcproc>
    </tsi>
</isis>
